fields.summary: Unmatched acknowledge (end of ack) , when connect to AMQ using WS over Stomp

comments.body: It looks like your client is attempting to ACK a message that was not dispatched to it, or perhaps attempting to ACK a message that was sent to it on a previous connection, neither of these would work and will generate the error you are seeing.
Not enough information provided to reproduce this one.
